.TH SIMPLE_SHELL 1 "MAY 2026" "Simple Shell Project"
.SH NAME
simple_shell \- A basic UNIX command line interpreter
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ./hsh
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B simple_shell
is a SH-compatible command language interpreter that executes commands read from the standard input or from a file.
.SS Invocation
The shell can be invoked in interactive and non-interactive mode.
.SH FEATURES
- Display a prompt and wait for the user to type a command.
- Execute commands with arguments.
- Handle the PATH.
- Built-in commands: exit, env.
